Question: On which side of the image is the couch?

Reference Answer: The couch is on the left of the image.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n554880.jpg

Program:

```
On which side is A?
Program:
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='all')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='couch')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'right' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'left'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
